<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ftḥ ʿynk kwys wbṣ ʿly̱ qdạm wrạ yswʿ bkẖṭwẗ ntqdm llạ̉mạm
 ạlqrạr- wạ̉kyd wạ̉kyd rạḥ tbqy̱ sʿyd ạ̉yạmk frḥẗ wklhạ ʿyd
 wmạdạm yswʿ ạlqạỷd rạḥ ybqy̱ ạlnṣr ạ̉kyd
 2- wạlwdn ạftḥhạ kwys wạsmʿ ạlklạm wmhmạ yqwl lk nfdẖ ttmtʿ bạlslạm
 3- wmạtnsạsẖ tṭlb mnh yḥfẓ lk ạllsạn wʿly̱ bạb sẖfạyfk yjʿl ḥạrs kmạn</lyrics>
